title: Migrant dispute overshadows Commonwealth reunion
text:
Migrant dispute overshadows Commonwealth reunion 3:39pm BST - 01:55 
A dispute over the residency rights of the so-called 'Windrush Generation' has dented UK plans to use a Commonwealth summit as a showcase for the country's global links. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
